scopeContent.description:
1) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-9. Group Mr Bourchier sitting at left of picture, in front of tall screen, Mr Mills standing, modelling a plaster figure'.

2) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-10. Group of six, all standing, looking at gentleman who is pointing & looking at bust of man'.

3) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-12. Group of six, five people seated round table, gentleman (Mr Bourchier) standing, looking down at other gentleman all standing, looking at gentleman (Mr Douglass)'.

4) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-13. Group of four persons, Mr Frank Mills, standing holding MIss Bateman's hands, Miss Vanbrugh standing looking away from them, Miss Grimston standing near door'.

5) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-14. Group of three, Miss Vanbrugh standing by table, leaning against it, Miss Bateman & Miss Grimston standing facing each other'.

6) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-15. Group of six, Mr Bourchier leaning over gramophone on table, Miss Bateman in white dress dancing'.

7) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-16. Group of two, Miss Vanbrugh sitting, looking up at Mr Bourchier, standing by her side'.

8) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-17. Group of three, gentleman standing, speaking at telephone, on left of picture, two ladies standing, looking at him, laughing'.

9) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-1. Group of three, gentleman lying back in wicker chair, with lady (Jessie Bateman) behind him, & lady sitting at right of picture on garden seat'.

10) 'Photograph of 'The Golden Silence', 1/1 plate size No 40296-2. Group of two ladies, Miss Bateman standing in white dress, Miss Grimston standing behind her, holding out her rigth hand'.
